    "biography": "<p>A slow-moving venomous Awakened viper (Vipera pseudocanis aspis) that nests and ambushes lone wanderers. Its mimicry can act as a hypnotic song with a slight change of tone.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Concealment (Personal), Enhanced Senses (Thermographic Vision), Mimicry (Special), Venom</p><p><em>Attacks: 3L, Reach −1 (venomous bite). Habitat: Very varied, mountains to coast; prefers grasslands. Range: France and Italy, northern Spain; especially the Alps and Pyrenees. 2D6 Initiative dice. Book Intelligence 2/4. PAE p.37.</em></p>",
